{"tid":289204,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人係睇英美劇學英文？","createTime":"2017-06-18T19:32:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T18:13:02.000Z","uid":58935,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2ca06b83696e417de7588b43ed2766c8fbeab407","tid":289204,"uid":58935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T19:32:36.000Z","msg":"想主動接觸多d英文 睇下劇嚟充實自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 字幕係中英 英 定冇字幕比較有效<br />\n<br />\n2. 聽唔明/唔識d vocab嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n逐句停查字典 <br />\n定由佢繼續講？因為有d嘢重複講可能會get到？<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以分享下經驗 用咩方法學英文 <br />\n或者仲有咩要注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97b26a62f9846fee3708fda5f58395c3981a216","tid":289204,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T19:33:59.000Z","msg":"我覺得有齊中英比較好<br />\n冇字幕根本唔知佢做緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28a0141bd84659923ea932f08ba802827f32d27d","tid":289204,"uid":58935,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T19:36:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得有齊中英比較好<br />\n冇字幕根本唔知佢做緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n開中英會唔會不自覺淨係睇中文"},{"pid":"4875e8233690f2fb431b8b853cf189c1a7777b0f","tid":289204,"uid":1248,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T19:41:38.000Z","msg":"用中文睇一兩次明大概講咩<br />\n之黎用英文係咁聽係咁repeat<br />\n聽唔明睇英文原稿<br />\n聽到自己滿意為止<br />\n<br />\n不過我係睇小說，上網搵audiobook<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0c86ef98da2de547a98aaca7074dbe67aa8f08b","tid":289204,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T19:44:15.000Z","msg":"唔好開中文字幕 淨係睇英文<br />\n唔識就先用查中文意思<br />\n之後耐左就試下用英英字典"},{"pid":"09ba1d25409c604d444d4bf3ba09f4c350e69dba","tid":289204,"uid":75870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T19:45:19.000Z","msg":"個人覺得睇字幕學英文個轉換應該係咁<br />\n1）中英字幕  <br />\n方便掌握vocab 但要強迫自己望英文個字幕<br />\n<br />\n2）英字<br />\n開始睇得明7成既時候就全英，會見到好多生字<br />\n<br />\n3）中字<br />\n淨睇中字既原因係比你訓練listening 去到呢個階段你會發現自己無左字幕根本咩都聽唔明 中文字幕可以輔助你去驗證自己理解到既野<br />\n<br />\n4）無字幕<br />\n最後一步<br />\n<br />\n利申 個人經驗 9up"},{"pid":"7a100f8fd645a93910047ede09ba8647f42a41c3","tid":289204,"uid":58935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T19:51:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用中文睇一兩次明大概講咩<br />\n之黎用英文係咁聽係咁repeat<br />\n聽唔明睇英文原稿<br />\n聽到自己滿意為止<br />\n<br />\n不過我係睇小說，上網搵audiobook<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小說應該好多vocab<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇用生字簿之類嘅嘢記低 <br />\n定係逼自己記入腦 <br />\n遲下就算唔記得 查到記得為止好d?"},{"pid":"95d6852759ab8f07255dace3ffafee82f4e46e93","tid":289204,"uid":1248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T20:10:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用中文睇一兩次明大概講咩<br />\n之黎用英文係咁聽係咁repeat<br />\n聽唔明睇英文原稿<br />\n聽到自己滿意為止<br />\n<br />\n不過我係睇小說，上網搵audiobook<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小說應該好多vocab<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇用生字簿之類嘅嘢記低 <br />\n定係逼自己記入腦 <br />\n遲下就算唔記得 查到記得為止好d?</blockquote><br />\n由淺入深<br />\n<br />\n我個做法係<br />\n會查生字，不過唔會寫解釋係個生字隔離，只會highlight佢<br />\n逼自己repeat個陣用腦諗返出黎<br />\n<br />\n因為我會將本小說斬件，每part都會repeat睇同聽好多次，所以自自然然會記得，唔會好似默書咁背生字<br />\n<br />\n如果真係怕唔記得可以做生字簿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5db7bd9e887665eb1543a7d350aeab99a10e4d5","tid":289204,"uid":61922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T22:21:18.000Z","msg":"上youtube睇walking dead(drama or game)<br />\nCOD 單人，學到嘅生字會practical D，睇岩phrase或者句子不彷搵本notes抄低，唔怕柒可以睇片跟住讀。"},{"pid":"43afde8410e73a72a2e9cc26aeb461fd1c80f0a2","tid":289204,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T22:36:10.000Z","msg":"我用黎學廣東話"},{"pid":"9886903f24e48fb84fcd287092fdd0394826e6e2","tid":289204,"uid":36533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T22:51:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eca27eabd65cb5e4d544ff92ca3983fa2f2a6eca","tid":289204,"uid":8922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T22:54:13.000Z","msg":"我廢，無記性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n生字學唔到幾多<br />\n但口音改善左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"193d80af2a9a79ccb0e3cdbbea248da55efa4e23","tid":289204,"uid":57406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:15:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我廢，無記性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n生字學唔到幾多<br />\n但口音改善左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我認同<br />\n中學個陣有睇開英美劇個d同學d口音係好d同講得順暢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8fe8ff65f2c1a7b1930c863cfa5d1e2aa83780f","tid":289204,"uid":97598,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:45:55.000Z","msg":"其實學好英文應該多管齊下。<br />\n<br />\n睇英美劇/電影、Youtube(歌片、打機片、電視節目、vlog等等)、新聞(BBC, ABC, SCMP, Young Post)、雜誌 (Economist, New York Times, TIME Magazine)、書(fiction, non-fiction)<br />\n<br />\n呢啲都係一啲普及嘅學英文渠道,大部分只要有電腦就做到<br />\n坊間補習社教嘅英文大部分不可取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b9bf15414aa96e735be03bd521b5481794ef98","tid":289204,"uid":88928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T10:17:56.000Z","msg":"開頭我係search 條片有無中文字幕翻譯黎睇， 但之後聽得多慣左YouTuber講野既速度之後我就係開英文字幕既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家有時會覺得條片太慢仲會開1.5倍速黎睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66cc43bd9dec628d44e28a48331eb6ab466478f6","tid":289204,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T10:26:32.000Z","msg":"英美劇對聆聽能力有幫助<br />\n<br />\n但教唔到發音<br />\n反而仲混亂咗 唔明點解咁讀<br />\n譬如英文連讀、略讀、合音等現象<br />\n<br />\n正確發音始終靠國際音標<br />\n文法係要腳踏實地學習"},{"pid":"69f8d36645ef6d92f67a52e45dd91928ff338b27","tid":289204,"uid":114097,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T10:30:47.000Z","msg":"睇完學到嘅只有 <br />\nDamn it <br />\nFuck you <br />\nOh Shit<br />\nWho the hell do you think you are <br />\nWhat the hell is wrong with you <br />\nScrew you<br />\nWhat the heck<br />\nYou son of the bitch <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84f4f1a92e586141afd7e5b4ae35cd21d22f0853","tid":289204,"uid":39001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T10:33:57.000Z","msg":"咁岩睇正vin diesel果啲咁嘅含撚嘴就真係食得屎"},{"pid":"ac188b09e84a0f9c0caeda9291d2209d3288e5ad","tid":289204,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T10:40:42.000Z","msg":"睇左幾季乜撚都學唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629af1da6ffa76af99248a53de6dee1321b542fc","tid":289204,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T10:41:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f0f8e02fb79937f6f286378c505d92feeebd1fe","tid":289204,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T12:33:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係有底進步 唔係無去有"},{"pid":"4aff2d510782b79421c3576fda7bcd7461618172","tid":289204,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T12:38:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好開中文字幕 淨係睇英文<br />\n唔識就先用查中文意思<br />\n之後耐左就試下用英英字典</blockquote><br />\n十句查一都無心機睇啦"},{"pid":"caa5bd13a7f748fbe2e3218bd8fd92438573dd0f","tid":289204,"uid":51313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T13:14:33.000Z","msg":"睇劇睇書都有好多生字唔識<br />\n但有d字根本自己係極少機會係日常生活用得番"},{"pid":"5fc4667d80329bb9ea6c6621d2af2ce08fd1cda5","tid":289204,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T18:05:28.000Z","msg":"1<br />\n要上手用英文字幕好d<br />\n慢慢捉到個語感同節奏<br />\n我試過練listening 一集睇咗兩次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一次認真睇，一次齋聽<br />\n一開始無字幕你聽唔明就無心機睇落去<br />\n<br />\n如果真係想試無字幕，可以睇YouTube 片或者綜藝節目<br />\n例如Master Chef<br />\n用字簡單同生活化d<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2 <br />\n我個時做法係先抄低，之後再查字典"},{"pid":"9f09b207cec19d52d3c9ac70d955195f5d1b1f4f","tid":289204,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T18:10:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我覺得有齊中英比較好<br />\n冇字幕根本唔知佢做緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n開中英會唔會不自覺淨係睇中文</blockquote><br />\n信我<br />\n一定會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}